title: (Thurs Full) We Share Our Favorite Heartbreak Songs + Amy Takes Her Quiz after Losing the Wheel of Anime
itunes:title: (Thurs Full) We Share Our Favorite Heartbreak Songs + Amy Takes Her Quiz after Losing the Wheel of Anime
description:
We go around the room and share our favorite Heart Break songs of all time. Amy lost the wheel of anime last week and had to watch 3 episodes of “Naruto”. She takes a quiz today to make sure she watched it.
